{"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllInputTextComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent09InputTextB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeinputtextcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"metadata":{"title":"OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B37ThemeInputTextComponentTokensProviderC","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider"}],"modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of input text","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"input text","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSInputText","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllInputTextComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"InouttextComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"input text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Inout text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), colors (","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for input text component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomInpuTextComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeInpuTextComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the input text component tokens you want.","","        override var inputTextSizeMaxWidth: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension3000 }","","        override var inputTextSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineShort }","","        override  var inputTextColorBgDefaultFocus: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomInpuTextComponentTokensProvider: InpuTextComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomInpuTextComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(inputText: CustomInputTextComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(inputText: CustomInputTextComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"name":"Since","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.10.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:colors:spaces:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeInputTextComponentTokensProvider\/InputTextComponentTokens-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"references":{"doc://OUDS/documentation/OUDS/TokensProvider":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"TokensProvider"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Protocol to add to any semantic or component tokens provider so as to be gather with all providers and given to the theme for initiali